vote.title: Authorize Supplemental Agreement No. 2 to the Dallas Memorial Auditorium Resident Use and Incentive Agreement (CCT-2024-00024819 No. 24-0616) with Full Court Partners LLC, d/b/a/ Dallas Wings to include (1) an addition of the address for secondary facility at 1200 North Cockrell Hill Road; and (2) additional negotiation terms. -  Financing: No cost consideration to the City
